  "text": "Similarly, orbit classification has also been conducted in celestial mechanics and dynamical astronomy regarding planetary systems. In particular, the orbital dynamics of the Earth-Moon system with two degrees of freedom using a scattering region around the Moon has been studied in [CITATION_1] .",
